data.title: Blogger: Nutzerprofil: Gerry Hannah
data.meta_description: Blogger ist ein Veröffentlichungs-Tool von Google, mit dem du ganz einfach deine Gedanken der Welt mitteilen kannst. Mit Blogger kannst du problemlos Texte, Fotos und Videos in deinem persönlichen Blog oder deinem Team-Blog veröffentlichen.
data.text:
Über mich

Geschlecht Männlich Standort Vancouver, Kanada Einführung I'm a musician (aka.Gerry Useless), the former bass player from the Subhumans (Canada) and I currently play rhythm guitar and sing with my own band playing my original compositions. I'm also into the bush and political activism. Interessen Indie Music, Hiking, Camping, Political Issues, Environmental Issues, Getting into Trouble, Getting out of Trouble, Reading Good Books, Laying on the Grass in the Sun, Writing and Playing Music from the Heart (with the volume on 10!), Reality, Fantasy Lieblingsfilme Steppenwolf, Love and Anarchy, Where the Green Ants Dream, The Weather Underground, The Filth and the Fury, The Decline of Western Civilization, Train Spotting, Drugstore Cowboy, Marat/Sade, Fahrenheit 9/11, If, The Idiots, Fubar, Hedwig and the Angry Inch, The Corporation Lieblingsmusik The Velvet Underground, Kurt Vile, The Sex Pistols, Stereolab, Camper Van Beethoven, PJ Harvey, Heavy Vegetable, Sebadoh, Brian Eno, Lucinda Williams, The Clash, Rob Crow, The Pogues, Subhumans, Jimi Hendrix, Joanna Newsome, Henryk Gorecki, Vaselines, Arvo Part
